column5: hey guys im up here in the ottawa valley and will be up here till end of jan. wondering if anyone has tried any of the lakes up here or the ottawa rive ice fishing. not lookin for hot spots just wondering what kind of fish are in them.  thanks guys
Petrie Island whenever it freezes up good.
Calabogie area is awesome.  Walleye, pike,  perch and monster rock bass can be had.
